  "title": "Clinic Executive #81832",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Healthcare Clinic</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Clinic Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Novena (8mins walk from Novena MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon-Fri: 9am-6pm, Sat: 9am-2pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic up to $3,800</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support daily clinic operations and provide a professional, patient-friendly experience.</li><li>Manage patient registration, records, referrals, appointments, and follow-ups (via calls/WhatsApp).</li><li>Handle medication dispensing, stock checks (including expiry), and basic assistance with clinical setup/equipment.</li><li>Coordinate surgery-related arrangements, including schedules, tests, ward bookings, and theatre coordination.</li><li>Support billing and administrative documents, including MOH-aligned financial counselling, insurance matters (e.g., LOG/claims), and preparation of reports/memos.</li><li>Liaise with hospitals and suppliers/vendors for urgent cases and required medical items.</li><li>Maintain a clean, safe clinic environment and ensure patient privacy and confidentiality.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in a specialist clinic or hospital setting is a strong advantage.</li><li>Good communication skills, patient-focused, and able to multitask in a clinic environment.</li><li>Knowledge of insurance panels is beneficial.</li><li>Familiar with appointment systems, medication dispensing, and basic clinical procedures.</li><li>Positive attitude, responsible, and strong willingness to learn.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81832 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
